  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to determine whether a significant reduction in the total level of
      alpha-synuclein and significant increase in the oligomeric form of alpha-synuclein and
      therefore the ratio oligomeric:total alpha-synuclein occurs in patients with Parkinson
      disease compared to patients with drug-induced parkinsonian syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
